  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You infuse an object - traditionally a broom, but any vaguely broom-shaped object (like a staff, spear, or similar) can be used - with flying magic, turning it into a Broom of Flying (basic rules, pg. 156).</p>\n<p>If your broom is lost or destroyed, you can create a new one during 8 hours of work. If a previous broom still exists when you make a new one, it loses its magic upon the completion of the new one.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>FoundryVTT</strong>: Manually drag a @Item[UmMenjJC5uGYvH6q]{Broom of Flying} onto the character sheet.</p>",
